txt.en: 'I commend your efforts, [placeholder]! Come, let us return and report our success to the Free Peoples.'
Use the Call Radhril skill and talk to Radhril
'I'll never strike it rich with you always mucking about!'
You should defeat the ruffian captain.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>
You have been tasked with destroying the brigand blockade within the mines of Writhenset.
Use the summoning horn at the beginning of the tunnel to summon Radhril to your side.
You should talk to Radhril.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>

You should retrieve stolen supplies and find a way to unlock the barricades.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>If Radhril is missing, and the Call Radhril skill is not available, try using the /pet release command.</rgb>

'I see, it looks as if the brigands have barred and locked themselves into the mines. This poses a more difficult task then I had envisioned. I am sure there is a way to unlock these gates. One of these brigands must hold a key. While we are here, we should also retrieve some of the goods that the brigands have stolen.'
Found the key to unlock the first barricade
Found the key to unlock the second barricade
Found the key to unlock the third barricade
